article.description: Diago Quinn recorded 14 points and 10 rebounds to lift Monmouth to a 73-59 win over Canisius in the semifinals of the Metro Atlantic Athletic Conference tournament on Sunday night.
article.headline: Quinn lifts Monmouth past Canisius 73-59 in MAAC tourney
article.linkText: Quinn lifts Monmouth past Canisius 73-59 in MAAC tourney
article.story: ALBANY, N.Y. -- Diago Quinn recorded 14 points and 10 rebounds to lift Monmouth to a 73-59 win over Canisius in the semifinals of the Metro Atlantic Athletic Conference tournament on Sunday night. Deion Hammond had 19 points for Monmouth (14-20). Marcus McClary added 10 points. Mustapha Traore had eight rebounds for Monmouth. Ray Salnave, who led the Hawks in scoring heading into the contest with 12 points per game, shot only 13 percent for the game (1 of 8). Takal Molson had 17 points and seven rebounds for the Golden Griffins (15-17). Jalanni White added 11 points.
